abstract: >-
  A comprehensive benchmark framework for systematically evaluating
  defenses against Indirect Prompt Injection (IPI) in tool-using LLM
  agents. Provides 565 test cases across 6 attack types and 54 injection
  techniques, implementations of 11 defense strategies (D0-D10), and
  automated evaluation across 4 frontier LLMs with statistical analysis.
  Includes Contextual Integrity Verification (CIV 2.0), a novel
  multi-signal defense combining prompt framing with risk-stratified
  tool gating.
